{"tid":411223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一食野就停唔到！！！！！","createTime":"2017-09-23T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T17:22:58.000Z","uid":136658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44f34fef0ec39d8d969466b6a175bb329bfb7503","tid":411223,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"呢個問題困擾左我好耐<br />\n有時明知訓前唔好食野我就係都要食<br />\n心諗 食一㗳就會停 但一食就會食左勁多<br />\n例如一盒蛋卷 我本身想食一舊就算<br />\n點知就食左成盒<br />\n食完又會再揾其他餅同零食食<br />\n內心不斷同自己講夠喇<br />\n之後就會飲返杯可樂/檸檬茶作結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係經常性 大概一星期一次咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸bmi 25 瘋狂食完會做返運動<br />\n朋友成日話我食少啲就減到肥<br />\n但我真係控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2c7448b840893a400f5d1fe19a67e998396f5f","tid":411223,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:35:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22e0fdeb58cdaa0205d1788085ddad1450920879","tid":411223,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"補充 時間通常係夜晚12點後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86744d5651db9696aedad0a3bfa92ec4332d160","tid":411223,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我食我男朋友條腸都係噉，一食就停唔到！</blockquote><br />\n又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103692f48e7291a3e86d4edfff9c1a4eb3bb8701","tid":411223,"uid":16104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:22:58.000Z","msg":"25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}